spec_data.Name: mariadb-config
spec_data.License: GPLv2 with exceptions and LGPLv2 and BSD
spec_data.Description:
The package provides the config file my.cnf and my.cnf.d directory used by any
MariaDB or MySQL program. You will need to install this package to use any
other MariaDB or MySQL package if the config files are not provided in the
package itself.

spec_data.Summary: The config files required by server and client
